00:57:54,099 --> 00:57:55,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

843
00:57:56,099 --> 00:57:57,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

844
00:58:00,269 --> 00:58:04,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat atas pernikahanmu.</font>

845
00:58:05,899 --> 00:58:10,961
<font color=#FFFF00>Hakim Lee Dong Joon.</font>

846
00:58:26,599 --> 00:58:28,599
<font color=#FFFF00>"Seorang hakim memperkosa
