847
00:58:28,639 --> 00:58:33,735
<font color=#FFFF00>"...yang meminta bantuannya."</font>

848
00:58:35,399 --> 00:58:36,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana menurutmu?</font>

849
00:58:38,039 --> 00:58:39,339
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutmu apa yang akan
terjadi pada si hakim?</font>

850
00:58:44,899 --> 00:58:46,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Shin Young Joo./
Tutup mulutmu.</font>

851
00:58:53,439 --> 00:58:58,282
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus membebaskan ayahku.</font>

852
00:59:00,939 --> 00:59:03,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Hakim Lee Dong Joon.</font>

853
00:59:15,864 --> 00:59:22,169
